      "type": "markdown",
      "location": "header",
      "position": "before",
      "content": "## Overview\n\nArcade.dev LLM tools for Microsoft OneDrive enabling programmatic access to a user's OneDrive to manage files, folders, sharing, search, and drive/user metadata via OAuth2-authenticated Microsoft APIs.\n\n**Capabilities**\n\n- Copy, move, and delete files or folders (supports async copy with status monitoring).\n- Create folders and generate share links for items.\n- List folder contents and enumerate items shared with the current user.\n- Search the user's OneDrive and retrieve item metadata.\n- Retrieve drive and user context (GetMyDrive, WhoAmI).\n\n**OAuth**\n\nProvider: microsoft\n\nScopes: Files.Read, Files.ReadWrite, User.Read"
    }
  ],
